  Wayne fixed the audio bug which causes severe video breakup.

  Debugging hang problem with SeaChange server:
    Control task stack very closed to overflow, doubled its size.

  Added check to see whether all tasks are successfully created, by checking
  only the last one.

  Need to increase heap size (in hw.cmd).  Heap is used for all task's stacks.
